    (32, 2, "Vedalken mature slower than humans do, reaching maturity around age 40. Their life span is typically 350 years, with some living to the age of 500."),
    (32, 3, "Vedalken are usually lawful and non-evil."),
    (32, 4, "Tall and slender, Vedalken stand 6 to 6.5 feet tall on average and usually weigh less than 200 pounds. Your size is Medium."),
