    (33, 2, "Aarakocra reach maturity by age 3. Compared to humans, aarakocra don’t usually live longer than 30 years."),
    (33, 3, "Most aarakocra are good and rarely choose sides when it comes to law and chaos. Tribal leaders and warriors might be lawful, while explorers and adventurers might tend toward chaotic."),
    (33, 4, "Aarakocra are about 5 feet tall. They have thin, lightweight bodies that weigh between 80 and 100 pounds. Your size is Medium."),
    (33, 5, "Your base walking speed is 25 feet."),
    (33, 11, "You can speak, read, and write Common, Aarakocra, and Auran."),
