    (35, 1, "Your Constitution score increases by 2."),
    (35, 2, "Genasi mature at about the same rate as humans and reach adulthood in their late teens. They live somewhat longer than humans do, up to 120 years."),
    (35, 3, "Independent and self-reliant, genasi tend toward a neutral alignment."),
    (35, 4, "Genasi are as varied as their mortal parents but are generally built like humans, standing anywhere from 5 feet to over 6 feet tall. Your size is Medium."),
    (35, 5, "Your base walking speed is 30 feet."),
    (35, 11, "You can speak, read, and write Common and Primordial. Primordial is a guttural language, filled with harsh syllables and hard consonants."),
    (35, 12, "Four major subraces of genasi are found among the worlds of D&D: air genasi, earth genasi, fire genasi, and water genasi. Choose one of these subraces.");
